        {
            "title": "人行明將進行5000億元人幣MLF操作 期限為1年",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行公布，將於明日以固定數量、利率招標、多重價位得標方式進行5000億元人民幣MLF(中期借貸便利)操作，期限為1年期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950123-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%98%8e%e5%b0%87%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c5000%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3mlf%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c-%e6%9c%9f%e9%99%90%e7%82%ba1%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 17:20:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "三一重工今遞來港IPO申請 曾傳集資規模達15億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大型A+H新股陸續有來，港交所(00388)資料顯示，三一重工(600031.SH)已遞交來港上市申請。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三一重工官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">早前市場曾傳出，三一重工今次捲土重來發H股上市，集資規模約達15億美元。資料顯示，三一重工曾於2011年提出來港上市，但最後因市況而擱置有關計畫。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一重工的初步招股書顯示，今次發H股上市由中信里昂證券任整體協調人。該公司成立於1994年，是創新驅動的全球工程機械行業領軍企業。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三一重工官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據弗若斯特沙利文的資料，按2020年至2024年核心工程機械的累計收入計算，三一重工是全球第3大及中國最大的工程機械企業。於往績記錄期間，該公司產品已銷往全球150餘個國家和地區，2024年海外市場收入佔總收入的62.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一重工母公司擁有人於2022年、2023年及2024年度應佔利潤，分別達43.01億元(人民幣．下同)、45.27億元及59.75億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950067-%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%80%e9%87%8d%e5%b7%a5%e4%bb%8a%e9%81%9e%e4%be%86%e6%b8%afipo%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b-%e6%9b%be%e5%82%b3%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e8%a6%8f%e6%a8%a1%e9%81%9415%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 17:15:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌283點   科技股推低大市  比特幣概念逆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後趺幅擴大，跌破上午低位，科技股成跌亦元兇，內需股也受壓，比特幣概念股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23544，跌283點或1.19%，今早開市報23748點，跌79點或0.33%，最高見23778點，跌49點或0.21%，隨即向下，午後跌破上午低位，見23470，挫357點或1.5%，為全日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_PO_source_web_Paul-chan3-e1747710513553.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_PO_source_web_Paul-chan3-e1747710513553.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20231205_fi_比特幣_source-licensed_.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20231205_fi_比特幣_source-licensed_.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：周大福官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_PO_source_web_Paul-chan3-e1747710513553.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20231205_fi_比特幣_source-licensed_.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：周大福官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日跌90點或1.7%，報5251點，今早開報5336點，跌5點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8557，跌103點或1.19%，今早以8640點開市，跌20點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報23502，跌281點或1.18%，低水42點 ; 科指期貨全日報5258點，跌82點或1.54%，高水6點 ; 國指期貨報8568，跌91點或1.05%，高水10點。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市全日成交1982.29億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技股偏軟拖低大市，小米(01810)跌2.3%，報53.2元，成交居首 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)跌3.25%，報119.1元；騰訊(00700)跌0. 77%，報516.5元；三股合計拖低恒指108點。美團(03690)跌0.95%，報136元；百度(09888)挫4.01%，報82.65%，摩根士丹利下調2025/12026盈利預測1%及10%，目標價由100美元降至95美元。野村指第二季指引令人失望。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想(00992)挫5.45%，報9.57元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代(03750)回吐，全日跌2.25%，報329.8元，對比A股仍溢價11.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">汽車股個別發展，比亞迪(01211)回吐1.38%，報456.2元，對恒指影響為13點。小鵬(09868)季績理想，升5.8%，報82.05元。 </p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_PO_source_web_Paul-chan3-e1747710513553.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_PO_source_web_Paul-chan3-e1747710513553.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">寧德時代在港掛牌上市。政府新聞處影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比特幣突破11萬美元，再創新高，相關概念股及ETF造好。博雅互動(00434)升6.37%，報6.18元 ; 華夏比特幣(03042)升3.84%，造13.81元；南方比特幣(03066)漲4.56%，造38.5元；博時比特幣(03008)彈高4.28%，收報8.655元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20231205_fi_比特幣_source-licensed_.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20231205_fi_比特幣_source-licensed_.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里健康(00241)收跌6.42%，報4.52元，為表現最差藍籌股。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內需股受壓，海底撈(06862)跌4.43%，報15.1元 ; 百威亞太(01876)跌4.13%，報7.66元 ; 華潤啤酒(00291)報24.95元，跌2.65% ; 農夫山泉(09633)跌2.73%，報36.7元，今日除淨。  </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福(01929)升4.37%，報11.46元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)再破頂，最高見229元，升6.02%，為上市以來高位，收升3.33%，報223.2元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：周大福官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950003-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c283%e9%bb%9e-%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e8%82%a1%e6%8e%a8%e4%bd%8e%e5%a4%a7%e5%b8%82-%e6%af%94%e7%89%b9%e5%b9%a3%e6%a6%82",
