        {
            "title": "港元拆息全線向下   H按息率跌破2厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息全線向下。與樓按相關的一個月拆息(HIBOR)跌至0.66613厘，連跌5日，再創近3年低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_FB_2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_FB_2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以現時一般新造H按計劃「H+1.3厘」計算，今日H按實際按息已跌至1.966厘，跌穿2厘水平，也創3年低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以平均按揭額400萬元，25年計，封頂息每月供款20025元，H按息每月供款16896元，較封頂息月供少3129元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜息0.02833厘，跌0.744基點 ; 1期報0.23292厘，跌0.756基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3個月拆息報1.70976厘，跌0.869基點 ; 6個月拆息報2.5667厘，跌4.047基點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14949739-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8b-h%e6%8c%89%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e8%b7%8c%e7%a0%b42%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 15:36:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息續跌  1個月拆息跌20基點  H按息率2.0578厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14945907&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元同業拆息續跌，與按揭利率相關的一個月拆息創2022年7月15日以來近3年低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241023_CR_SSP4_source-bp_01-e1738826613533.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/703x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241023_CR_SSP4_source-bp_01-e1738826613533.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據香港銀行公會公布最新香港銀行同業拆息(HIBOR)，與按揭利率相關的1個月拆息報0.7578厘，跌20.26基點，創2022年7月15日以來近三年低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜拆息報0.03577厘，升0.91基點 ; 一星期拆息0.24048厘，跌3.67基點</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3個月拆息1.80845厘，跌17.88基點 ; 6個月拆息2.61714厘，跌17.41基點</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">12個月拆息3.22071厘，跌4.52基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">H按的按揭息率H+1.3厘計，現時按揭息率為2.0578厘，低於封頂利率的3.5厘。以貸款400萬元，還款期25年計，封頂息每月供款20025元，H按每月供款17067元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14945907-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e7%ba%8c%e8%b7%8c-1%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e8%b7%8c20%e5%9f%ba%e9%bb%9e-h%e6%8c%89%e6%81%af%e7%8e%872-0578%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 15:15:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
